Package compiler.symboltable

Class SymbolInfo

java.lang.Object
compiler.symboltable.SymbolInfo
public class SymbolInfo extends Object
Contains information about a high-level-language Symbol with a specific Type that is saved at a specific location in memory and, if it is a variable or a constant, has a varType (e.g. int, string).

Two high-level-language Symbols are considered identical if and only if their keys are equal.

Author:
Alex Mandelias
